BONGA NET encrypts your Internet connection so that third parties can’t track your online activity, making it more secure than a typical proxy, make your Internet's safety and security, especially when you using public free Wi-Fi.

We have built a global VPN network included America, Europe and Asia, and expand to more country soon. Most servers are free to use, you can click the flag and change server as any times as you want.

Main Features
Proxy service

Super-fast, super-lightweight, and easy to use

If the BONGA NET is helpful for you, please rate us 5 stars ⭐ ⭐ ⭐ ⭐ ⭐
